{"word":"G3489 - ναυαγέω - nauagéō - now-ag-eh'-o - Make shipwreck","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ναυαγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nauagéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">now-ag-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make shipwreck</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கப்பலைச் சேதப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to suffer shipwreck"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3491 - ναῦς - naûs - nowce/3491\">G3491</a> and <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to <i>be shipwrecked</i> (<i>stranded</i>, &ldquo;navigate&rdquo;), literally or figuratively: - make (suffer) shipwreck.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}